Checks if pois in the same category is ovelapping each other.

If so it removes the latest from the map.

Parameters:
gfxMap The map containing all the poi data.
params Needed for getting the lowest scale and for calculating the tileBox.
refTileMap Used for snapping the coords of a feature to a correct pixel.
desc Used for getting info about the feature etc.
poiCache Cache containing allready calculated poi:s
avoidSet POIs that shouln't be included in the map is added to this list.
